   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i Nilfloden.</text:span></text:p>
