   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭlŏgræcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Grekwän, wän af grekisk literatur:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏlāus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭlŏlŏgus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏlŏgus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: wän af studier l. lärdom, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Witter, lärd;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos sednare serskildt = wän l. idkare af literaturhistoriska l. historisktantiqvariska studier, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">philolog:</text:span></text:span> homines nobiles illi quidem, sed minime p-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lärde),</text:span> C.; quum Ciceronis librum de Republica prehendit hinc philologus, hinc grammaticus, hinc philosophiæ deditus, - philosophus miratur contra justitiam dici tam multa potuisse, - philologus subnŏtat, quem nos dictatorem dicimus, apud antiquos magistrum populi vocatum, grammaticus - <text:span text:style-name="T1">reapse</text:span> dici a Cicerone in commentarium refert, Sen. Ep. 108; p. est, qui multiplici variāque doctrinā censetur, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ämnen l. skrifter: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lärd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som röjer l., för att förstås, fordrar beläsenhet): (ss. gr. ord,</text:span> φιλολογώτερα), C.; Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏlŏgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kärlek till) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lärdom, lärda studier:</text:span></text:span> C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos sednare serskildt = wittra, literaturhistoriska l. antiqvariska studier, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">philologi:</text:span></text:span> quæ philosophia fuit, facta philologia est (i. e. studium non animum excolendi, sed ingenium), Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭlŏmēla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Näktergal:</text:span></text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. person, som förwandlades till en näktergal.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏmēlĭum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Phrygien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phĭlŏmēlensis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phĭlŏmēlĭensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏmētor, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏmūsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlōnĭdes, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlōnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏpător, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏpoemen, mĕnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏsītus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭlŏsŏphus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wishet älskande:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏphus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏpha</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wishetswän</text:span></text:span> (= sapientiæ studiosus, Cic. Tusc. V. 4.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">philosoph:</text:span></text:span> qui expetunt sapientiam, p-i nominantur; qui, ceteris omnibus pro nihilo habitis, rerum naturam studiose intuerentur, Pythagoras p-os appellabat; p-orum inventa; magnus, summus, doctus, gravis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grundlig),</text:span> severus, summo ingenio, exquisitā doctrinā, summā auctoritate p.; Socratis multiplex ratio dicendi - plura genera (familias) effecit dissentientium philosophorum; veteres p-i; p-i disputant, disserunt; disputatio p-i; Socratici; omnia gymnasia p-i tenent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upptaga);</text:span> audire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afhöra, studera under)</text:span> p-um; p-o operam dare; ea villa tamquam p-a videtur esse, quæ objurget ceterarum insaniam, C.; schola p-i; discipulus p-i, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Philosophisk:</text:span></text:span> Mcb., Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏphe</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På philosophiskt sätt, philosophiskt:</text:span></text:span> C. (Acad. I. 8. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Halms conjectur).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏphĭa</text:span>, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wishetskärlek, philosophi</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. wetenskap l. lefnadswishet):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> nihil aliud est p. præter studium sapientiæ; omnium laudatarum artium procreatrix quædam et quasi parens p.; p. ars vitæ, cultura animi; vera, perfecta p.; p-æ nomen quibusdam invisum est; p-æ multum temporis tribuere; p-æ operam dare, se dare; in p-ā operam studiumque ponere, versari; ea, quæ tractantur in p-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(philosophiska ämnen),</text:span> de p-ā scribuntur; hi de p-ā libri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(philosophiska skrifter);</text:span> ea, quæ in p-ā dicuntur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(philosophiska satser);</text:span> hæc sunt penitus in media p-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sjelfwa hjertat af p.)</text:span> retrusa atque abdita; p-am vituperare, accusare, defendere, collaudare; p-am Latinis literis illustrare; singulæ p-æ disciplinæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(philosophiska system, läror);</text:span> quum omnia in p-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(philosophiska frågor),</text:span> tum id, quod hic quæritur; homo eruditus in p-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med philosophisk bildning);</text:span> p-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om p.)</text:span> scriptiones; p. in tres partes est tributa, in dis serendi subtilitatem, in naturæ obscuritatem, in vitam atque mores, C.; p. moralis, Sen. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Ep. 16).<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Philosophisk skola</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lära:</text:span></text:span> antiqua et nobilissima p. (Peripateticorum); ea p., quæ suscepit patrocinium voluptatis; hæc exercitatio propria est duarum p-arum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏphĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Philosophisk:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏphĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Philosophiskt:</text:span></text:span> C. (d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŏsŏphor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">impers.,</text:span> Pt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Studera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (idka) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">philosophi, philosophera; på philosophiskt sätt behandla ett ämne;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tänka, tala som en philosoph:</text:span> p-ndum est, sed paucis, nam omnino haud placet, Enn. ap. C.; p-atur homo, Pt.; quibusdam totum hoc displicet p-ri; p-ndi scientiam multis concedo; quid opus est in hoc p-ri?, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭlostorgus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öm mot anhörige:</text:span> Fr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlōtas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭlŏtechnus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Konstmässig:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlŏtīmus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭloxĕnos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Philtrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kärleksdryck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hĭlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. familjenamn i</text:span> gens Furia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phĭly̆ra</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phĭlŭra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lindbast, bastlager:</text:span></text:span> nexæ p-ā coronæ, Hor.; papyrum divisum in tenuissimas philuras, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phĭly̆rēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till Ph. l. hennes son Chiron hörande.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phĭly̆rĭdes, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Chiron.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phīmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tärningsbägare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwarur tärningarne kastades):</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hīneus, ĕos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ĕi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phīnēĭus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phīnēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phīnīdes, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hintĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hintĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phlĕbŏtŏmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åderjern, lancette.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phlĕbŏtŏmĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phlĕbŏtŏmĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åderlåtning.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phlĕbŏtŏmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åderlåta:</text:span></text:span> Veg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hlĕgĕthon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i underjorden.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phlĕgĕthontēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phlĕgĕthontis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f. A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phlegethontisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hlĕgon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af solens hästar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hlĕgra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Macedonien, der Giganterne krossats af blixten.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phlĕgræus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hlĕgy̆as, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hlīus, untis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Achaja.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phlīāsĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hŏbētor, ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förskräckare): en drömgud:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phōca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phōcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skälhund:</text:span></text:span> Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hōcæa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Ionien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcæensis, <text:line-break/>Phōcā̆ĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phocæisk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcæi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i Ph.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcā̆is, ĭdis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phocæisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hōcĭon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hōcis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Grekland.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcensis, is, <text:line-break/>Phōcĕus, <text:line-break/>Phōcĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i Ph.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcēus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phōcīus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phocisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hōcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phoebas,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af Phoebus inspirerad qwinna, spåqwinna:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hoebē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. = Diana.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. och historiskt qwinnonamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hoebus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">solguden (solen),</text:span> Apollo. <text:line-break/>Phoebēĭus, <text:line-break/>Phoebēus, <text:line-break/>Phoebĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phoebĭgĕna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af Phoebus född, Phoebi son:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hoenix, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phoenicier. -</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">fem.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hoenissa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phoeniciska.</text:span><text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fågeln </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Phoenix,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som, ensam i sitt slägte, hwart hundrade år troddes komma från Orienten till Aegypten och der reda sitt bål, hwarefter en ny</text:span> phoenix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uppstod af den förbrände kroppen:</text:span> T. A. 6. 28.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hoenīca, æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phoenīcē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phoenicien.</text:span><text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Epirus:</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>Phoenīcĕus <text:line-break/>(Poenīceus), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Purpurröd:</text:span></text:span> Lucr. <text:line-break/>Phoenīcĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phoenicisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phoenīcoptĕrus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rödstjert,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> Flamingo (fågel):</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Phoenissa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Phoenix 1.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hŏlŏē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Thracien</text:span><text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hŏlos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phōnascus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr. (φωνή, ἀσκεῖν): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sånglärare, lärare i declamation:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>horbas, antis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>horcus, i, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phorcys, y̆os, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phorcyn, ȳnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phorcȳnis, ĭdis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phorcis <text:line-break/>(Phorcys), ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phorci dotter (Medusa).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hormĭo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hŏrōneus, ĕi (ĕos), <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. konung i Argos.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phŏrōnēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phŏrōnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phoroneus’ dotter</text:span> (Io, Isis).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phosphŏros,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljusbringaren, morgonstjernan:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hrăātes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hrăhātes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">parthiskt konunganamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phrăsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttryck; stil</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lat.</text:span> elocutio): Sen.; Qu. X. (§. 42).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phrĕnēsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanwett:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phrĕnētĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanwettig;</text:span></text:span> C., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hrixus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phrixēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: mare = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Hellespontus (öfwer hwilken wäduren med det gyllne skinnet samm med P.).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Phrygia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. m. se</text:span> Phryx.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hrȳnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hryx, Phry̆gis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i äldre latin</text:span> Brux, Brugis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phryger (folkslag i mindre Asien, ofta = Asiat i allm.).</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hry̆gĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Phrygien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phry̆gĭo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som förfärdigar phrygiskt guldstickningsarbete, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Guldstickare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phry̆gĭōnĭus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: vestes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med phrygiskt guldstickeri).</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hry̆gĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phrygisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hthas, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ægyptisk gudomlighet</text:span> (Vulcanus): C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hthīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hthīas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hthīōtes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phthīōta, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är från Phthia.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hthīus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hthīōtĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">phthiotisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phthĭsis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twinsot:</text:span></text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phthĭsĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">behäftad med twinsot:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phy,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Interj.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fy!:</text:span></text:span> Ter. Ad. 412.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phy̆lăca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fängelse:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hy̆lăcē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. stadsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phy̆lăcēis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af - .</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phy̆lăcēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phy̆lăcĭdes, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">son af, bördig från P.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phy̆lăcista,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fångwaktare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phȳlarchus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(asiatisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stamfurste, -höfding:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hȳlē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fästning i Attica.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hȳleus, ĕi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hyllis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hyllĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hyllŏdŏcē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hyllos, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Grekland.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Phyllēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thessalisk.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>hyscon, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillnamn för Ptolemæus</text:span> III.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Phy̆sis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Natur:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till naturen hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Naturwetenskaplig, naturphilosophisk:</text:span></text:span> C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Naturphilosoph:</text:span></text:span> C. (Tusc. I. c. 20, de Fin. I. 6.).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭca</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Naturphilosophi:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På naturphilosophernes sätt, i deras mening:</text:span></text:span> p. dicere de vi igneā, de calore; fatum est non id, quod superstitiose, sed quod p. dicitur, causa æterna rerum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭognōmon</text:span>, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Physiognomist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som ur menniskors anletsdrag tror sig kunna bedöma deras character):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Phy̆sĭŏlŏgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Naturlära, -philosophi:</text:span></text:span> dum haruspicinam veram esse vultis, p-am totam pervertitis; p. id est naturæ ratio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Piabilis, Piacul . . ., Piamen, -amentum, -atio, -atrix <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skata:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Picaria, Picea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pix.<text:line-break/>Picens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Picenum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īcentia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Campanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pīcentīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īcēnum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap på östra kusten af Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pīcens, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">picenisk, Picener.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pīcentīnus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pīcēnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">picenisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Piceus, Pico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pix.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>ictāvi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Aquitanien (Poitou).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pictāvĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>icti, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i Britannien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pictilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pingo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>ictŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span> = Pictavi. <text:line-break/>Pictŏnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pictor, -tura, -turatus, Pictus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pingo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īcumnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gudomlighet.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hackspett:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; Martia avis, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gudomlighet, enl. sagan en konung, som förwandlats till en hackspett.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pie <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īĕrĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landskap i Macedonien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pīĕrĭus, <text:line-break/>Pīĕrĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pierisk, macedonisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īĕris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af Pierus.</text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. Musa: C. (de Nat. Deor. III. 21. 54.). <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en konung Pieri, med Muserna liknämnda, döttrar:</text:span> Ov. Met. V. 310.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pietas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pius.<text:line-break/>Piger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Piget.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĭget,</text:span> uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ĭtum est, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">V. Imp.</text:span> (pigere interdum pro tardari, interdum pro poenitere poni solet, Fs.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T1">alqm</text:span> piget <text:span text:style-name="T1">facere alqd</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gitter icke, har olust, motwilja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kan ej få sig till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att -</text:span> (non p-et = juvat): p-et dicere, his annis viginti quam ludibrio fueritis superbiæ paucorum; quæ fecerit, incertum habeo, pudeat magis an p-eat disserere, Sa.: p-bat fateri, non esse in sua potestate Latinos, L.; possim multa - præcepta referre, ni - tenues p-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försmår att)</text:span> cognoscere curas; non me meminisse p-bit Elissæ, dum memor ipse mei -, Vg.; juremus in hæc, ne conversa domum p-eat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wägra)</text:span> dare lintea, quando Padus Matina laverit cacumina, Hor.: p-uit ultra portas procedere, Ppt.; p-et esse pium, Ov.; ire, Mt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T1">alqd</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott då saken är</text:span> neutr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> pron.) p-et <text:span text:style-name="T1">alqm</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förargar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">alicujus rei</text:span> p-et <text:span text:style-name="T1">alqm</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förargar sig, harmas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kan ej lida, är</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. (i perfectformerna) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blir ledsen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(ångrar)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> pol pudere quam p-re præstat; p-et fecisse, Pt.; id me p-et; facti p-et, Ter.; tui me miseret, mei p-et, Acc. ap. C.; stultitiæ me non solum p-et, sed etiam pudet; ad pudendum, ad p-dum induci, C.; me civitatis morum p-et tædetque, Sa.; p. incepti lucisque, Vg.; Pæti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid P. ss. befälhafware)</text:span> piguerat, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgendus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wärd att harmas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blygas) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ångra):</text:span> causas habet error honestas: adde fidem, nullā parte p-us erit, Ov.; poscis ab invitā verba p-a lyrā, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭger</text:span>, gra, grum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ej gitter, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dorsk, lat, lätjefull,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dåsig, slapp), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beqwäm:</text:span></text:span> ad scribendum; in re militari p. et timidus, C.; gens (Gallorum) ad militaria opera p-a, L.; optat ephippia bos p.; nihil habeo, quod <text:soft-page-break/>agam, et non sum p., usque sequar te; p. scribendi ferre laborem; militiæ (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>) p. et malus, Hor.; mane p. stertit, Ps.; p-um et iners videtur (Germanis) sudore acquirere, quod possis sanguine parare, T.; secessus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stilla boning),</text:span> qui facit dominum p-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(obenägen för resor),</text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Håglös, olustig:</text:span></text:span> ad poenas p., ad proelia velox; pectus, Ov.; vultus, Mt.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stel, dåsig, domnad, orörlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (slapp, matt); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">långsam</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">långsamt gående, flytande m. m.; äfwen om saker, som förorsaka dessa egenskaper (anfördt bland exempel på</text:span> denominatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(metonymi)</text:span> C. ad Her. IV. 32), p-um frigus, quia facit p-um)]: apes frigore pigræ, Vg.; campi p-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(frusna),</text:span> Hor.; p-um rigorem affert bruma, Lucr.; mare p. et prope immotum, T.; alvus p., Ce.; hiems p-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den frusna),</text:span> Ov.; sopor, Catl.; senecta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slapp, kall),</text:span> Tib.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om tid l. i tid) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långsam:</text:span></text:span> p. annus videtur pupillis, Hor.; bellum, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utan drift</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fart; olustigt, ogerna:</text:span></text:span> agere, Col.; ire ad mortem, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgreo</text:span>, 2.:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgresco</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara, blifwa lat, stel, orörlig:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgrĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgrĭties</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Olust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för rörelse l. arbete, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tröghet, lätja, dåsighet, dorskhet; beqwämhet:</text:span></text:span> p. et metus consequentis laboris; p-ā non scribere, C.; p. militandi, L.; ingenua p. (= otium poētæ), Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kroppslig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slapphet:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgro</text:span> (Acc.),<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭgror</text:span> (C.), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara lat, dröja:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Impĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oförtruten, rask, flitig, hurtig:</text:span></text:span> ad labores; se præbere i-um et patientem; in scribendo, C.; vir, N.; ingenium, Sa., C.; militia, L.; equus, mercator, Achilles, Hercules; i. hostium vexare turmas, Hor.; i. militiæ, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Impĭgre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oförtrutet, raskt, hurtigt:</text:span></text:span> res suas attendere, Sa.; sequi, se movere, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Impĭgrĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Raskhet:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pigment . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pingo.<text:line-break/>Pigner . . ., Pignor . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pignus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pignus,</text:span> ŏris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pant, underpant, säkerhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i rättsliga förhållanden: pant, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gißlan:</text:span></text:span> p-i opponere aliquid <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätta i pant),</text:span> Pt., Ter.; p. dare, accipere; p-ora aufert ab senatore magistratus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att twinga honom till att biwista sammanträden l. bryta hans opposition);</text:span> p-a cædit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sönderhugga, förstöra, wid fortsatt tredskande,</text:span> de Or. III. 1.); senatores p-bus cogere, C.; p-a capere, L.; p. pacis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gißlan för freden),</text:span> L., Vg.; fidem alicujus p-e obligare, Ct.; rem p-ori <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i pant)</text:span> accipere, T.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insats</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid ett wad:</text:span> p. dare in alqd <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätta upp, hålla på ngt),</text:span> Pt.; tu dic, mecum quo p-ore certes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med hwilken insats du will täfla, hwad du sätter upp),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pant, underpant</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = allt, hwarmed ngn förbinder l. </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förpligtar sig till ngt (band, löfte) l. bekräftar, bewisar ngt, öfwertygar ngn (bewis):</text:span> reipublicæ p. dedit, se liberam civitatem esse velle, quum dictaturam sustulit; habet a M. Caelio respublica duas accusationes, p-ora voluntatis; - pro libertate projicias fortunas, tamquam p-ora injuriæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(panter på oförrätt</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som oundwikligt utsätta dig för - -),</text:span> C.; p-ora da, genitor, per quæ tua vera propago credar; p-a certa, Ov.; (equum Ascanio Dido) esse sui dederat monumentum ac p-us amoris; has olim exuvias mihi - reliquit p-ora cara sui, Vg.; hæc Amor ipse suo constringet p-era <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbund)</text:span> signo, Ppt.; p. dereptum lacertis aut digito, Hor.; sedes Jovis (ɔ: Capitolium) - a majoribus tanquam p. imperii condita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(d. w. s. Jupiter hade genom att emottaga templet gifwit pant på -),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt kallas barn och andre </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anhörige:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> trohets-, kärleks-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">panter, underpanter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. band på ömsesidig trohet och tillgifwenhet:</text:span> (famæ pignora, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på makas rykte, ära);</text:span> nunc tibi commendo communia p-ora natos, Ppt.; tot natos natasque et, p-ora cara, nepotes, Ov.; per carissima p-a (liberos, conjugem, parentes), Qu.; (privigni) proxima suis p-ora; in conjugem, in familiam et cetera p-ora alicujus sævire, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ett träds skott, ympqvist,</text:span> Pal.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pignĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taga i pant, utpanta:</text:span></text:span> p-tum habere aliquid, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sätta, gifwa i pant, förbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lofwa:</text:span></text:span> bona, L.; ad impensas unionem, Su.; se coenæ, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pignĕror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taga i pant, tillegna sig:</text:span></text:span> Mars ex acie fortissimum quemque p-ri solet, C.; omen pigneror, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pignĕrātīcius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som angår pant; pantsatt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som lånar l. lånas mot pant:</text:span> actio; fundus; creditor, Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pignĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pantsättning:</text:span></text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pignĕrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Panttagare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pignŏriscăpio</text:span> (pignoris capio), ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pantning:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oppignĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sätta i pant, pantsätta, förpligta:</text:span></text:span> filiam, Ter.; libellos pro vino, C.; anulum octo numis, Mt.; se o., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Præpignĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i förwäg taga i pant; binda:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rĕpignĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Återinlösa pant:</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pigr . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Piger, Piget.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĭla,</text:span> æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: rund kropp, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klot, kula, boll:</text:span></text:span> lanuginis, Pn.; p-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rofwor)</text:span> Nursinas esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äta),</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Boll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att leka, spela med:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. uttryck:</text:span> p-am dare, Næv.; p. lusoria, Pn. (XII. 57); p-ā ludere; p-æ studio teneri, C.; p-æ pictæ, Ov.; p-am mittere, excutere, excipere, accipere, remittere, repercutere, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck:</text:span> dii nos quasi p-as homines habent; mea p. est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jag har wunnit),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Himmelsglob:</text:span></text:span> Ppt. IV. (V.) 1. 76.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kula,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarmed voterades wid domstol:</text:span> in mea sortitā vindicet ossa pilā, Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kula</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af bernsten l. ngt wälluktande ämne, hwarmed damer höllo sina händer kyliga:</text:span> manibus durā frigus habere p-ā, Ppt.; Mt.<text:line-break/>6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">menniskofigur af hö l. halm, som dels utsattes s. offer åt underjordens makter</text:span> (Fs.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dels på amphitheatren anwändes till att reta wilda djur:</text:span> taurus jactat cornu p-am, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: lusio p., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Boll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-spel:</text:span> St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jonglör, taskspelare:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I tät massa:</text:span></text:span> Serv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopträngd, tätt sluten:</text:span></text:span> agmen, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlicrĕpus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (crepo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Boll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">- (-smällare) -</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">spelare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> expulsim): Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten kula, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pill:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Præpĭlatus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om lans l. wärja) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I ändan afrundad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">försedd med boll:</text:span></text:span> missile, L.; hasta, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pīla <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pinso.<text:line-break/>Pila Horatia, Pilanus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pilum, Pinso.<text:line-break/>Pilaris, -larius, -latim <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pĭla.<text:line-break/>Pilatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pĭla <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Pilum, Pinso. <text:line-break/>Pileatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pileus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīlentum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fyrhjulig, betäckt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wagn</text:span></text:span> (currus arcuatus), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i hwilken matronor, Vestaler,</text:span> Flamines <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åkte till gudstjenst, fester m. m.:</text:span> matronis datum est, ut p-is ad sacra ludosque, carpentis festo profestoque uterentur, L.; castæ ducebant sacra per urbem p-is matres in mollibus, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pileolus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pileus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīleus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīleum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(halfäggformig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Filthufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hatt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utan skyfwen) för män (begagnad under arbete i fria luften, på resor m. m.; på konstwerk attribut för sjömän och handtwerkare, deraf för</text:span> Ulysses <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Vulcanus):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> Pt.; Tarquinio in carpento sedenti - aquila - p-um aufert et rursus capiti apte reponit, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">emedan den frigifne slafwen till tecken af sitt nya stånd anlade</text:span> p., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är:</text:span> ad p-um vocare, p-o donare = in libertatem vindicare, libertate donare alqm, Pt., L.; hæc mera libertas, hæc nobis p-a donant, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīleātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klädd i hufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hatt:</text:span></text:span> fratres p-i (= Castor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Pollux, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. sjöfarandes beskyddare),</text:span> Catl.; turba p-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(folkmassan wid</text:span> Saturnalia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">då man satt till bords i</text:span> pileus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. ett frihetstecken),</text:span> Sen.; morte Neronis plebes p-a (quasi libertatem adepta) discurrebat, Su.; servi p-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid en slafauction de, för hwilkas trohet säljaren ej wille answara),</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīleŏlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hatt:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Impīlia</text:span>, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Filtskor:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pilicrepus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pĭla.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>ilius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>ilia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: T. Pomponii Attici <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hustru.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Pilo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plundra:</text:span></text:span> Amm. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> Pĭlus? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. stamverb till</text:span> Compīlo, Expīlo, Suppīlo?).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Pĭlo, Pilosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pĭlus.<text:line-break/>Pilula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pĭla.<text:line-break/>Pilum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pinso.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īlumnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fornitalisk konung:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (på hwilken del af menniskas l. djurs kropp som helst):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> palpebræ munitæ sunt vallo p-orum, C.; p. (capitis), Phdr.; p. caudæ equinæ, Hor.; plurimus p. est homini, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildliga uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ett hår</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ett grand, det minsta:</text:span></text:span> ne p-um quidem boni viri habet; ne p-o quidem minus; ne p-um quidem a Cappadocia (discedere), C.; alqm non p-i facere, Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra hårlös, raka:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hårbewuxen, luden:</text:span></text:span> genæ, C.; folia p-ora, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dēpĭlātus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dēpĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skägglös:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pīlus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pilum, Pinso.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>impla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ort (berg l. källa) i Macedonien.</text:span> (Varro l. l. VI. 2.). <text:line-break/>Pimplēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Muserna tillhörig.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pimplēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pimplēis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: = Musa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīna</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Pinna), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mußla:</text:span></text:span> C., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĭnăcŏthēca,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭnăcŏthēcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tafle-, målningsgalleri:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īnārius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fornromerskt slägtnamn:</text:span> L. I. 7. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>inăros, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Cilicien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pinaster <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pinus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pincerna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">munskänk:</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>indărus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn, berömdt genom den lyriske skalden P. från Thebæ, i 5:te seklet före Christus.</text:span> Pindărĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>indĕnissus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Cilicien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pindĕnissītæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inwånare i P.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>indus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg mellan Thessalien och Epirus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pinea, Pinetum, Pineus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pinus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pingo,</text:span> pinxi, pictum, 3.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm.: anbringa bilder på en yta,</text:span> Pn. XXX. 5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bilda l. afbilda med linier och färger</text:span> (penicillo)); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afmåla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> tabula picta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(målning),</text:span> C., Sa.; taurum, speciem hominis, Helenæ simulacrum p.; Alexander se ab Apelle potissimum p-i volebat; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: måla, idka målarekonst</text:span> (Tusc. I. 2.), C.; picti <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tatowerade)</text:span> Agathyrsi, Vg.; proelia picta; suspendit pictā mentem vultumque tabellā, Hor.; picti metus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott målade skräckbilder),</text:span> Ppt. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: med ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måla:</text:span></text:span> Pompejum omnibus pinxi artis coloribus; Britanniam p-gam coloribus tuis, penicillo meo, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra slags bilder:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rita, teckna:</text:span></text:span> e tabula pictos ediscere mundos, Ppt. (IV. 3. 37.); levi virgā in spisso litore alqd, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sticka, utsy, brodera:</text:span></text:span> stragulum pictum, C.; acu p-re; pictæ vestes, Ov.; toga, Ppt.; tapeta, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sira</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med utskurna </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bilder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i träd l. i metall af inlagdt l. drifwet arbete</text:span> (= cælare): picta arma, Vg. (Aen. VIII. 588. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> X. 499.); picta neque inducto fulgebat parma pyropo, Ppt. (IV. 10. 21.) <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">måla = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färga, brokigt sira</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smycka:</text:span></text:span> humum floribus, Pt.; tempora frontemque sanguineis moris; vaccinia calthā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(brokigt blanda med -),</text:span> Vg.; puppes pictæ, Hor.; conchæ p-unt terram, Lucr.; litora collucent nativis picta lapillis; armorum radiis picta tremebat aqua, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pictus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brokig:</text:span></text:span> volucres p-æ, Vg.; arcus (Iridis); pavo, Ov.; cauda pavonis p-a, Hor.; pluma, Phdr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om framställning) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sirlig, utsirad:</text:span></text:span> orationis genus; Lysiā nihil p-ius est, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pictĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsydd, stickad:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pictor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Målare:</text:span></text:span> p-es et ii, qui signa fabricantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(målare och bildhuggare),</text:span> C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen tillnamn i</text:span> gens Fabia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pictūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Målare-, teckningskonst; målning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i concret mening):</text:span> ars ratioque p-æ; p-ā uti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utöfwa); -</text:span> nego ullam p-am fuisse (in Sicilia), quin conquisierit (Verres), C.; animum p-ā pascit inani, Vg.; ut p-a, poēsis: erit, quæ, si propius stes, te capiat magis, et quædam, si longius abstes, Hor.; certamen p-æ; p. linearis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(teckning),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stickeri, utsydd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wäfd teckning:</text:span></text:span> p. in textili, C.; textilis, Lucr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: målning af phantasien l. med ord:</text:span> Homeri p-am, non poēsin videmus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det är målning, wi se, ej vers, wi läsa hos H.);</text:span> imagines p-aque virtutum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pictūrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stickad, utsydd:</text:span></text:span> vestis, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brokig:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pigmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. det, hwarmed man målar l. kan måla:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färg; smink:</text:span></text:span> C., Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">talets </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prydnad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med l. utan bibetydelse af ngt otillbörligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(smink):</text:span></text:span> Aristotelica; p-orum flores et color; sententiæ sine p-is fucoque puerili, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäxtsaft:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pigmentārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smink-, essencehandlare:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Appingo</text:span>, pinxi, pictum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måla till -, tillägga i en målning:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> qui variare cupit rem prodigialiter unam, delphinum in silvis <text:soft-page-break/>a-it, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i en skrift tillägga:</text:span> alqd novi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dēpingo</text:span>, pinxi, pictum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afmåla, måla:</text:span></text:span> pugnam in porticu, N.; tabellas, Ppt. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsy, sticka, brodera:</text:span></text:span> pænulam, Su. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i phantasien l. med ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra en målning af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">måla, skildra:</text:span></text:span> facta, Ter.; tabulam verbis; rempublicam in sermone d.; cogitatione alqd d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppgöra sig en bild, föreställning af),</text:span> C.; rerum imaginem verbis d., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Expingo</text:span>, pinxi, pictum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I målning framställa, utföra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> pericula, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildligt:</text:span> regio, motus hominum (verbis) e-ti, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färga, sminka:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pinguis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur och menniskor: fet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wälfödd, -mående, gödd:</text:span></text:span> agnus, Pt., Ov.; p-es Thebani et valentes, C.; lardum; aper p-is arundine, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mark och wäxter m. m.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fet, frodig, saftig, fruktbar:</text:span></text:span> solum, hortus, caseus, olivum, oleum, Vg.; ficus, Varr.; campus p-ior <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gödd)</text:span> sanguine; p-ia semina, palmeta; p-es rami, Hor.; tæda, Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf:</text:span> <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fettig, smord:</text:span></text:span> ara <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af offerfett),</text:span> Vg.; virga <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(limstång);</text:span> coma, Mt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> orator pexus p-que (= nitidus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">elegant),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wälmående, wäl försedd), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trygg, beqwäm:</text:span></text:span> quies, somnus, Ov.; mollis et p. vita - hoc est innoxia et beata; secessus, Pn. ep.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik, riklig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wäl försedd:</text:span> stabulum (apium), Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjock, grof</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">syn.</text:span> crassus): <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> caelum, C.; toga, Su.; aurum, Ps.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om uttal: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjock, bred:</text:span></text:span> Cordubæ nati poētæ, p-e quiddam sonantes et peregrinum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med ett eget bredt och främmande uttal),</text:span> C.; sonus, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om l. till förståndet (mots.</text:span> subtilis): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Enfaldig, olärd, dum:</text:span></text:span> agamus p-i Minervā (i. e. remota philosophorum subtilitate); hoc ipsi Antiocho p-e videbatur et sibi contrarium, C.; p-e pecus domino facies (Mercuri) et cetera præter ingenium; p-i munere donari, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om färg: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjert:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pingue</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fett:</text:span></text:span> densum, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguēdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fetma:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguĕfīo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguesco</text:span>, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa fet, gödas:</text:span></text:span> armenta, Col.; campi p-unt sanguine, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa oljig, glänsande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>3. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ökas:</text:span></text:span> Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguiārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som älskar fett:</text:span></text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguĭcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något fet:</text:span></text:span> Fronto. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fett; rikligt; enfaldigt:</text:span></text:span> Col., Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinguĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fetma:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bredt uttal:</text:span></text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjerthet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i färg:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Præpinguis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Owanligt fet:</text:span></text:span> sŏlum, Vg.; terra, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om uttal) owanligt, för mycket </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bred:</text:span></text:span> vox, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Subpinguis</text:span> <text:line-break/>(suppinguis), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något fet:</text:span></text:span> Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pinifer, Piniger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pinus.<text:line-break/>Pinna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Penna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Pina.<text:line-break/>Pinnatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Penna. <text:line-break/>Pinnicillus = Penicillus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Penis. <text:line-break/>Pinniger, Pinnirapus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Penna</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>innius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pinnŏtēres</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīnŏtēres</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Pīnŏthēras), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(som bewakar (jagar)</text:span> pina), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kräfta:</text:span></text:span> C. (de Fin. III. 19.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pinnula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Penna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pinso</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīso</text:span>, pinsui, pinsum, pinsĭtum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> pistum, 3.: (pinso <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> piso, 1., Varr.; <text:line-break/>pinsio, 4., Enn.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stöta, slå, hacka:</text:span></text:span> terram; flagro alqm, Pt.; Janum (ut bifrontem) a tergo nulla ciconia p-it, Ps.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sönderstöta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mortel), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-krossa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> [säd (med stöt - det ursprungliga sättet att bereda mjöl - jfr</text:span> pistor, -strīnum) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. annat för hushållet, murbruk m. m.]; om säd wäl äfwen = krossa i allm., äfwen = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mala</text:span></text:span> (Pn. XVIII 23.): neque pilo pinsui neque molā molui, poët. ap. Diom. gr.; pilo pinsunt far; uvam passam et ficum p., Varr.; hordeum, panicum, allium p-ĭtum; lens p-ĭta minuteque molita, Col.; pisente pilo præferrato; zea pista, Pn.; rudus pinsum; materiam pinsere, Vitr.; apud majores molæ usus non erat, frumentum torrebant et in pilas missa pinsebant, Serv. ad Vg. Aen. 1. 179.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mortel, tråg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwari man sönderstöter, bereder ngt):</text:span> pinsere triticum in p-ā; lignea, Cato; aromata in p-ā contundere, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pelare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fyrkantig, mots.</text:span> columna = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rundpelare, colonn):</text:span> p-as pontis locare in Tiberim, L.; in lapidea p-ā incidere alqd, N.; p-as operibus subdere, Sen.; nulla taberna meos habeat neque pila <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(der anslag gjordes om nya skrifter)</text:span> libellos, Hor. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dam, bålwerk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot watten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hamnbrygga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kaj):</text:span> p-am saxeam magnis molibus constructam ponto jaciunt, Vg.; congestis p-is turrim imposuit, Su.; Vitr. V. 12.; omnis in p-is Puteolorum turba consistit, Sen. (Ep. 77.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mortelstöt, stöt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. redskap):</text:span> pinsere far p-o, Cato, Varr.; pisente <text:soft-page-break/>p-o præferrato, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt (l. i allm. italiskt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kastspjut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gr.</text:span> ὑσσός), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kortare (ungef.</text:span> 5½ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fot), men fastare och tyngre än</text:span> hasta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gr.</text:span> δόρυ), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med skaft och jernspets af inbördes lika längd, tjenligt så wäl till att stöta, som till att slunga:</text:span> p. haud paulo vehementius ictu missuque telum, quam hasta, L.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> T. Ann. II. 14.; p. injicere alicui, Pt.; p-a mittere, immittere, conjicere in hostem, Cs., L.; plura hostium scuta uno ictu p-orum transfixa et colligata, Cs.; p-is missis ad manus (gladios) ventum est, L.; caput alicujus fixum gestare in p-o, C.; exesa rubigine p-a, Vg.; agmina p-is horrentia, Hor.; p-a acta femineā manu; stabant Romano p-a Sabina foro, Ppt.; p-a minantia p-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medborgare mot medborgare),</text:span> Luc.; p. torquere in alqm, Sen.; p. adigere alicui, Val.; - Pila Horatia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett ställe i Rom, der wäl ursprungligen Horatiernes</text:span> pila <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">upphängts efter striden med Curiatierne,</text:span> L. I. 27. Ppt. III. 2. 7. - vigilantia pila = vigilantes pilanos, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīlānus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">pilum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wäpnad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt</text:span> = triarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tredje linien):</text:span> Varr. (l. l. V. 89.), Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.: Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Manipel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">triarier</text:span></text:span> (pilani): L. VIII. 8. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt omtalas ofta</text:span> primus pilus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den förste manipeln</text:span> (primus ordo) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af triarier, hwars anförare hette</text:span> primi pili centurio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> primipilus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äfwen</text:span> primus centurio, L.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och sades</text:span> ducere primum pilum, Cs., L.; primus centurio, quem nunc primi pili (centurionem) vocant, L.; adimere alicui primum p., Su. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Primipilus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">under</text:span> Primus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Antĕpīlānus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som står framför</text:span> pili i. e. triariorum agmen, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">benämning för</text:span> acies hastatorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> principum, L. (VIII. 9.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pinsātio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīsātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stötning, kroßning:</text:span></text:span> Vitr., Sen. (d. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistillum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistillus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mortelstöt, -stock:</text:span></text:span> p-o fragrantia mollit allia; it p. in orbes, Vg. (Mor.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som stöter säd i mortel l. maler på handqwarn</text:span> (ad circumagendas molas trusatiles p-ori operam locavit Plautus, Gell. III. 3.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjölnare:</text:span></text:span> (apud antiquos) p. nomen erat ejus, qui ruri far pinsebat, Varr.; Pn.; p-es scrophipasci, qui furfuri alunt sues, Pt.; Jupiter p., Ov. Fast. VI. 350.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bagare:</text:span></text:span> coqui et p-es, C.: p. (= dulciarius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sockerbagare),</text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bagare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> opus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrīnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställe, der säd krossas l. males, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Handqwarn:</text:span></text:span> molere in p-o; alqm in p-um dedere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(straff för late och oduglige slafwar),</text:span> Ter.; in p-um detrudere, in p-o vivere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bildliga uttryck, om simpelt, mechaniskt arbete),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bageri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. yrke och ss. anstalt):</text:span> Pn.; exercere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(idka),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrilla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Handqwarn:</text:span></text:span> Ter.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrīnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till handqwarn hörande, der befintlig:</text:span> sues, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrīnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjölnare:</text:span></text:span> Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrīnensis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: jumenta, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dragare, som anwändas wid en qwarn:</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjölnerska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bagerska:</text:span></text:span> Lucil. ap. Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pistūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjölberedning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (genom stötning l. malning):</text:span> Pn. XVIII. 28.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Expinso</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utstöta, -mala:</text:span></text:span> far, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīnus,</text:span> us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(l.</text:span> i), <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fur; pinie:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> fraxinus in silvis pulcherrima, p. in hortis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(parker),</text:span> populus in fluviis, abies in montibus altis; p-os loquentes, Vg.; imminens villæ p., Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">helgad åt Cybele och Pan,</text:span> Vg., Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om saker, som äro af</text:span> p.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om skepp:</text:span> Pontica p., silvæ filia nobilis, Hor.; sacræ p., Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om facklor:</text:span> p. flagrans, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om spjut:</text:span> St. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åra:</text:span> Luc.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krans</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">furbarr,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> buren af Pan l. de isthmiske segerwinnarne:</text:span> Ov., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīnaster</text:span>, stri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wild fur:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīnea</text:span>, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pinieäple:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīnētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Furuskog:</text:span></text:span> gelidi Lyæi, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som är af fur l. pinieträd, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Furu-, pinie</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> silva; claustra, Vg.; cortex, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīnĭfer</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīnĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Furor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krans af furubarr bärande:</text:span></text:span> Mænalus, Vg.; caput Fauni, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pius.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pipa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Pipatus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Pipo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĭper,</text:span> ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Peppar:</text:span></text:span> album, Hor., Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭpĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pepprad:</text:span></text:span> Col., Petr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. om en tjuf:</text:span> non fuit Autolyci tam p-a (= acris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rask?)</text:span> manus, Mt. VIII. 59. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭpĕrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: lapis p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kornig sten,</text:span> it. peperino), Isid.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīpĭlo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pī</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">pio,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pipa:</text:span></text:span> passer, Ctl. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīpio,</text:span> 4.: id.: pulli, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīpo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pipa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (som en kyckling):</text:span> gallina, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīpātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pipande:</text:span></text:span> pullorum, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīpio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kyckling, dufunge:</text:span></text:span> Lpd. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīpŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīpŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">barns </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwidande:</text:span></text:span> Fronto.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrikande, gräl:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īræeus <text:line-break/>(Piræus, Catl.), ei, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (Πειραιεύς): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hamn och hamnstad</text:span> (demos) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till Athen, genom murar förenad med den öfre staden:</text:span> triplex Piræei portus, N.; <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc.</text:span> Piræea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Piræeum, C. <text:line-break/>Pīræus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">piræisk:</text:span> Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pīrāta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjöröfware, kapare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīrātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjöröfware tillhörig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjöröfware</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> bellum, C.; navis, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pīrātĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjöröfweri:</text:span></text:span> p-am facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(idka),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īrēnē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">källa wid Corinthus.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Pīrēnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f. A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Pirenes, pirenisk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">P</text:span>īrĭthŏus, ŏi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pĭrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Päronträd:</text:span></text:span> inserere, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pĭrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Päron:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Vg.; decerpere, Hor.</text:p>
