   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Piscis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fisk:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> p. nequam est, nisi recens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ny, frisk),</text:span> Pt.; p. ludit in aquā; p-es nancisci; p. corrumpitur, Ter.; p. capitur hamo; gignit ova; acipenser p. nobilis, C.; p-es captare, Ov.; p. vult natare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”fisken will simma”),</text:span> Petr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stjernbilder:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. pisces, p. gemelli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fiskarne):</text:span> Ov., C. <text:line-break/>b. p. major, p. aquosus, Avien., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> hamus, forum, Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskmånglare:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fisktorg:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
