   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fisk:</text:span></text:span> minuti, Ter.; parvi, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskdam:</text:span></text:span> mullulos exceptans de p-ā, C.; muraenas continere in p-ā, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wattningsdam, sump</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på l. wid en landtgård:</text:span> servit anseribus, Col. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sim-) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bassin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett badhus:</text:span> calida p. mirifica, ex qua natantes mare aspiciunt; si natare latius velis, in area est p., Pn. <text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wattentråg, ho:</text:span></text:span> lignea, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscīnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till bad hörande:</text:span> Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscīnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egare (och älskare) af fiskdammar:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiska:</text:span></text:span> hic p-ri nulli solent, C.; aureo hamo p-ri (minima commoda non minimo sectari discrimine), Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskande:</text:span></text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskare:</text:span></text:span> Ter., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fiskare tillhörig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-:</text:span> navis, Cs., L.; forum, Col.; casa, Petr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskareqwinna:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiske, fiskafänge,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. handling och i collectiv mening:</text:span> Pt., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fiskrik:</text:span></text:span> Vg.; amnis, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Piscŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.: locus, Pt.</text:p>
